00:30:19,359 --> 00:30:21,851
[Sayagues] It's makeup,
but he had to keep his mouth closed,

558
00:30:21,945 --> 00:30:25,483
because if he opened it,
the illusion would fail.

559
00:30:27,492 --> 00:30:29,108
[grunts]

560
00:30:29,202 --> 00:30:31,944
[Alvarez] That's me making the sound,
you can't hear it, but I went...

561
00:30:32,039 --> 00:30:34,155
[screeching]

