00:30:34,249 --> 00:30:37,833
We recorded it like this in the consensus
that we had some sounds that worked.

563
00:30:37,919 --> 00:30:40,035
They brought me a microphone
and I started to do it.

564
00:30:40,130 --> 00:30:43,122
-My contribution.
-[Luque] You did it like Mel Gibson.

565
00:30:43,216 --> 00:30:45,503
They say he does that in the sessions.

566
00:30:45,594 --> 00:30:49,132
[Alvarez] In the audio mix sessions
and things like that.

