00:31:13,538 --> 00:31:16,951
[Sayagues] Bobby added a lot
to that character.

575
00:31:18,377 --> 00:31:21,460
We had to restrain him
because he was always adding things,

576
00:31:21,546 --> 00:31:24,664
and we cut it a bit,
but what was left is great.

577
00:31:27,469 --> 00:31:29,051
[Luque] The Blind Man here...

