00:31:33,934 --> 00:31:35,424
Does he know that she is in the box?
Yes, he yelled at the box.

581
00:31:35,519 --> 00:31:39,513
[Alvarez] Well, I think he trusts that
she reached the box, but he isn't sure.

582
00:31:39,606 --> 00:31:42,724
[Luque] Phoenix is very well-trained.

583
00:31:42,818 --> 00:31:45,685
[Alvarez] He trusts that he trained
her well and that she has arrived.

584
00:31:45,779 --> 00:31:48,191
Especially if he hears noises
in the house still.

585
00:31:48,281 --> 00:31:52,024
They're in the house because
they haven't found her yet, right?

586
00:31:52,119 --> 00:31:53,735
If not, they would have already left.

587
00:31:55,539 --> 00:31:58,327
But this is also
one of the first times in the saga

588
00:31:58,417 --> 00:32:03,958
that you see him vulnerable, in trouble,
thinking about what he's going to do.

589
00:32:04,047 --> 00:32:07,460
[Luque] Of course. It was like the shark
was there. He didn't know where he was.

590
00:32:07,551 --> 00:32:09,508
[Alvarez] It appears and disappears
in general,

591
00:32:09,594 --> 00:32:12,052
but this is the first time
we started to see it.

592
00:32:12,139 --> 00:32:15,006
Only a little bit, because there are
very few windows the film gives you

593
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:16,761
to see what is happening with him.

594
00:32:18,353 --> 00:32:20,264
I love this shot, there it is.

595
00:32:24,443 --> 00:32:26,025
That shot from The Shining.

596
00:32:26,111 --> 00:32:28,478
[Luque] That shot from The Shining
always needs to be there.

597
00:32:28,572 --> 00:32:33,442
[Sayagues] Especially if you have an actor
with that look, you have to do it.

