00:33:31,176 --> 00:33:34,589
[Sayagues] Well, because we wanted
to put a patch

613
00:33:34,679 --> 00:33:38,798
with a half motorcycle logo
on this guy's back,

614
00:33:38,892 --> 00:33:43,227
and we thought, "Let's do
something Uruguayan that looks cute."

