00:33:43,313 --> 00:33:45,805
[Luque] And the truth is
that Alvacast's typography is great.

616
00:33:45,899 --> 00:33:48,857
[Sayagues] It's great. It looks very good
and it also meant something

617
00:33:48,944 --> 00:33:51,231
because I also moved a lot

618
00:33:51,321 --> 00:33:53,983
in that metal scene of those times,
so it was good.

619
00:33:54,074 --> 00:33:56,907
[Alvarez] Yes, and they are also
one of those pioneering bands

